# GraphQL - Get all categories with subcategories
POST {{Slingcessories.service_HostAddress}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ categories { id name subcategories { id name } } }"
}

###

# GraphQL - Get category by ID
POST {{Slingcessories.service_HostAddress}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ categoryById(id: 1) { id name subcategories { id name } } }"
}

