# GraphQL - Filter accessories by wishlist
POST {{Slingcessories.service_HostAddress}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ accessories(where: { wishlist: { eq: true } }) { id title price wishlist } }"
}

###

# GraphQL - Sort accessories by price
POST {{Slingcessories.service_HostAddress}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ accessories(order: { price: DESC }) { id title price } }"
}

###

# GraphQL - Complex query with filtering and sorting
POST {{Slingcessories.service_HostAddress}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ accessories(where: { wishlist: { eq: false } }, order: { title: ASC }) { id title price units category { name } } }"
}

